    public class ClientRealm
extends org.apache.shiro.realm.AuthorizingRealm
    This realm implementation is dedicated to authentication. It acts on credentials after the user authenticates at the provider and finishes the authentication process by getting the user profile from the provider.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Jerome Leleu
